name: INTERNAL_EVENT_PRODUCED_EXTERNAL_REPORT
description: The probe produced a log report for transmission to the backend for external analysis

name: INTERNAL_EVENT_LOG_ITEMS_MISSED
description: Some log items were overwritten without successfully getting reported to the collector, the number of missed entries is storedin the payload

name: INTERNAL_EVENT_LOGICAL_CLOCK_OVERFLOWED
description: A logical clock's count reached the maximum trackable value

name: INTERNAL_EVENT_NUM_CLOCKS_OVERFLOWED
description: The probe did not have enough memory reserved to store enough logical clocks to track all of the unique neighbors that attempt to communicate with it

name: EVENT_INSUFFICIENT_REPORT_BUFFER_SIZE
description: The report destination buffer is too small to fit a header and/or the frontier clocks

name: TOP_OF_THE_LOOP
description: At the top of the loop
